an> 標題：細麵粉（fine flour）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： סֹלֶת, קֶמַח</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： soleth, qemach soleth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:6\">GEN 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:6\">GEN 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:2\">EXO 29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:40\">EXO 29:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:1\">LEV 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:2\">LEV 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:4\">LEV 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:5\">LEV 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:7\">LEV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:11\">LEV 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:8\">LEV 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:13\">LEV 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:12\">LEV 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:10\">LEV 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:21\">LEV 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:13\">LEV 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:17\">LEV 23:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:5\">LEV 24:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:15\">NUM 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:15\">NUM 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:13\">NUM 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:19\">NUM 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:25\">NUM 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:31\">NUM 7:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:37\">NUM 7:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:43\">NUM 7:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:49\">NUM 7:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:55\">NUM 7:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:61\">NUM 7:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:67\">NUM 7:67</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:73\">NUM 7:73</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:79\">NUM 7:79</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:8\">NUM 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:4\">NUM 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:6\">NUM 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:9\">NUM 15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:5\">NUM 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:9\">NUM 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:12\">NUM 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:12\">NUM 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:13\">NUM 28:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:20\">NUM 28:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:28\">NUM 28:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:3\">NUM 29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:9\">NUM 29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:14\">NUM 29:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:19\">JDG 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:24\">1SA 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:24\">1SA 28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:28\">2SA 17:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:2\">1KI 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:2\">1KI 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:12\">1KI 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:14\">1KI 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:41\">2KI 4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:1\">2KI 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:16\">2KI 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:18\">2KI 7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:29\">1CH 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:41\">1CH 12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:29\">1CH 23:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:2\">ISA 47:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:19\">EZK 16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:14\">EZK 46:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:7\">HOS 8:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σεμίδαλις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： semidalis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:13\">REV 18:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir35:2\">SIR 35:2